ctu.nengoros.comm.nodeFactory.nativenode

Interface NativeNodeContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ExternalNodeContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RunnableNode, UNodeContainer

    public interface NativeNodeContainer
extends ExternalNodeContainer
    NativeNode should be able to create process by means of ProcessBuilder (ideally in a constructor) according to launchCommand and prepare it for starting. These nodes should support manual and auto-stopping.
